  "instructions": [
    "Heat a tava or griddle over medium-high heat.",
    "Add 1 tsp of sesame oil to the tava.",
    "Add the roasted sweet potatoes and cook for 2 minutes per side, or until caramelized.",
    "Add the roasted carrots and cook for an additional 2 minutes, or until heated through.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together gochujang paste, rice vinegar, grated ginger, and garlic to make the sauce.",
    "Add the sauce to the tava and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the caramel sauce and cook for 30 seconds, stirring constantly.",
    "Season with coarse salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Garnish with green onions, toasted sesame seeds, and fresh cilantro.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
